# PACAME — Vercel deployment ignore (Sprint 24 fix)
#
# Excluye los PNG originales pesados (180MB) de los assets generados.
# Solo se sirven los WebP+AVIF optimizados de /public/generated/optimized/ (~48MB).
# Los componentes ya importan desde /generated/optimized/<slug>.webp.
#
# Esto evita el cancel inmediato del deploy preview por exceder limites de tamaño.

# Generated PNG originals (kept in git for backup, not deployed)
public/generated/*.png
public/generated/agents/*.png
public/generated/services/*.png
public/generated/sectors/*.png
public/generated/cases/*.png
public/generated/og/*.png
public/generated/icons/*.png
public/generated/pattern/*.png
public/generated/mobile/*.png

# But INCLUDE optimized variants (WebP + AVIF responsive)
!public/generated/optimized/

# Build artifacts
.next/cache/
node_modules/.cache/

# Logs
*.log

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
